data.title: LL-1 - Universal Reloading Label for Rifle & Handgun Ammo Boxes 50 Pack
data.meta_description: The Load Labels are just what the conscious reloading shooter needs. Ample space is supplied for important information such as caliber, powder, bullet weights and primers. A special non permanent adhesive has been applied to the back of these stickers so you may remove sticker after changing load.
